Compiled for 32-bit with MinGW. A Code::Blocks project.

Playing around with FreeGLUT to create a simple game engine, using C.


Keys:
W,A,S,D - move
shift+W,shift+S - turn up/down
Q,E - turn left/right
ESC - Quit
F12 - Change keyboard layout recognition between QWERTY and DVORAK
+,- - Speed up or slow down the movement and turning

2012/01/28
-added keys to change movement and turning speeds, and changed the movement functions to reflect the changes
2012/01/27
-I use dvorak keyboard layout, so for easier testing I included a function key to change between the layouts, to get WASD working at the right part of the keyboard
